### ===========================
### API Origo — HTTP Client File
### ===========================
### Используйте с расширением REST Client (VS Code)
### или IntelliJ HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@origoUrl = https://api.origo.kz/api/v1
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE


### ───────────────────────────
### Health Check
### ───────────────────────────

### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health


### ───────────────────────────
### Auth
### ───────────────────────────

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@qtxample.com",
  "password": "password1234",
  "first_name": "Test",
  "last_name": "User"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}


### ───────────────────────────
### Products (public)
### ───────────────────────────

### List products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&page_size=20

###

### List products with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&page_size=10&category_id=1&min_price=100&max_price=50000&search=телефон

###

### Get product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1


### ───────────────────────────
### Products (admin — requires auth)
### ───────────────────────────

### Create product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "New Product",
  "slug": "new-product",
  "description": "Product description",
  "price": 9990,
  "stock": 50,
  "category_id": 1,
  "image_url": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "is_active": true
}

###

### Update product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "slug": "updated-product",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "price": 12990,
  "stock": 30,
  "category_id": 1,
  "image_url": "https://example.com/image-new.jpg",
  "is_active": true
}

###

### Delete product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ───────────────────────────
### Categories (public)
### ───────────────────────────

### List categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

###

### Get category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/1


### ───────────────────────────
### Categories (admin — requires auth)
### ───────────────────────────

### Create category
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "slug": "electronics",
  "description": "All electronics"
}

###

### Update category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Updated Category",
  "slug": "updated-category",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

###

### Delete category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
